276
00:15:48,090 --> 00:15:48,930
I...

277
00:15:52,210 --> 00:15:53,760
This is unexpected to me.

278
00:16:00,560 --> 00:16:02,800
How many cups of coffee have you had?

279
00:16:05,560 --> 00:16:06,450
Five.

280
00:16:07,060 --> 00:16:08,570
You still didn't sleep well last night?

281
00:16:08,570 --> 00:16:10,730
You've got dark circles
under your eyes like a panda.

282
00:16:11,390 --> 00:16:12,760
Stop trying to hold on.

283
00:16:13,160 --> 00:16:15,010
Ask for a leave and get some rest.

284
00:16:16,800 --> 00:16:18,730
If I could sleep, I would have already.

285
00:16:22,170 --> 00:16:24,520
What's Mr. Gao's conversation
with Ma Chao about?

286
00:16:24,520 --> 00:16:25,560
Why does it take so long?

287
00:16:27,730 --> 00:16:28,570
Xiuya.

288
00:16:31,560 --> 00:16:33,280
Did you hear what I said?

289
00:17:20,340 --> 00:17:23,040
(Notice of Ma Chao's promotion:
You've been promoted to team leader.)

290
00:17:29,890 --> 00:17:31,010
Anyone want milk tea?

291
00:17:35,560 --> 00:17:37,410
It's on me.

292
00:17:39,280 --> 00:17:41,280
The sun comes out of the west today,
doesn't it?

293
00:17:41,410 --> 00:17:43,210
When did you ever treat us?

294
00:17:43,560 --> 00:17:44,930
That's not true.

295
00:17:44,930 --> 00:17:46,280
You make it sound like I'm stingy.

296
00:17:46,280 --> 00:17:48,010
I treated you before.

297
00:17:48,800 --> 00:17:50,170
Did anything good happen to you?

298
00:17:52,730 --> 00:17:53,570
Nothing.

299
00:17:54,730 --> 00:17:56,170
No way. There must be something.

300
00:17:56,320 --> 00:17:57,160
Hurry and tell us.

301
00:17:59,170 --> 00:18:00,650
I can't tell you yet.

302
00:18:01,720 --> 00:18:04,010
Quit cutting around the bushes.

303
00:18:04,650 --> 00:18:05,730
I really can't tell you.

304
00:18:07,080 --> 00:18:08,890
Okay, I won't ask.

305
00:18:17,040 --> 00:18:18,010
It's nothing.

306
00:18:18,280 --> 00:18:20,210
Mr. Gao talked to me just now.

307
00:18:20,360 --> 00:18:22,170
He said
he would promote me to team leader.

308
00:18:23,280 --> 00:18:24,520
You must be lying.

309
00:18:24,800 --> 00:18:26,560
Haven't you always been self-aware?

310
00:18:26,560 --> 00:18:28,760
Why do you start daydreaming now?

311
00:18:29,760 --> 00:18:32,410
How can I lie about this?

312
00:18:32,680 --> 00:18:33,550
Come. Let me show you.

313
00:18:35,170 --> 00:18:36,010
This is the email.

314
00:18:36,730 --> 00:18:38,180
Good for you.

315
00:18:39,040 --> 00:18:40,880
You're only treating us to milk tea?

316
00:18:40,880 --> 00:18:43,250
You should treat us to Xinrong Ji.

317
00:18:43,360 --> 00:18:44,560
Right.

318
00:18:44,560 --> 00:18:45,560
You got promoted.

319
00:18:45,560 --> 00:18:47,170
You'll get a raise.

320
00:18:47,170 --> 00:18:48,560
You've got to treat us
to something good.

321
00:18:48,560 --> 00:18:49,420
Right.

322
00:18:49,430 --> 00:18:50,890
I just got a promotion.

323
00:18:50,890 --> 00:18:51,930
I didn't win the lottery.

324
00:18:52,240 --> 00:18:54,560
Besides,
we all know the size of the raise.

325
00:18:55,120 --> 00:18:56,560
Come. Let's have milk tea.

326
00:18:56,560 --> 00:18:58,600
Come on. It's on me.

327
00:18:58,600 --> 00:18:59,730
Pass it around.

328
00:19:00,280 --> 00:19:01,120
Come on.

329
00:19:01,250 --> 00:19:02,090
Order a set.

330
00:19:03,250 --> 00:19:04,450
- I'll have this.
- Okay.

331
00:19:04,450 --> 00:19:06,250
- Thanks, Chao.
- Come on.

332
00:19:06,250 --> 00:19:07,090
Lemon tea.

333
00:19:07,320 --> 00:19:08,600
It was obviously his problem.

334
00:19:09,010 --> 00:19:10,560
How come it became his credit?

335
00:19:10,760 --> 00:19:12,080
It's not fair.

336
00:19:12,080 --> 00:19:13,800
What is the management thinking?

337
00:19:15,010 --> 00:19:17,250
Xiuya, you need to talk to Manager Hu.

338
00:19:18,260 --> 00:19:19,610
What's the point of talking to her?

339
00:19:19,730 --> 00:19:21,800
Manager Hu knows what's going on.

340
00:19:22,490 --> 00:19:23,360
Thank you, Chao.

341
00:19:23,360 --> 00:19:25,120
You're welcome.

342
00:19:27,260 --> 00:19:28,660
Xiuya, what would you like to drink?

343
00:19:31,650 --> 00:19:32,490
No.

344
00:19:34,030 --> 00:19:36,010
It only takes a minute
to order milk tea.

345
00:19:36,280 --> 00:19:37,910
Getting work done is not the only thing.

346
00:19:38,140 --> 00:19:39,760
You need
to maintain a good relationship.

347
00:19:40,120 --> 00:19:41,450
Come on. Order one.

348
00:19:42,320 --> 00:19:43,600
You won't embarrass me, right?

349
00:19:43,860 --> 00:19:45,650
I'm stupid.
I just know how to get work done.

350
00:19:45,980 --> 00:19:47,300
I need some peace. Leave me alone.

351
00:19:56,800 --> 00:19:57,760
Okay.

352
00:19:58,520 --> 00:20:00,320
I'll go back now.

353
00:20:01,490 --> 00:20:02,560
He likes to take advantage.

354
00:20:10,410 --> 00:20:12,760
You didn't fill out the reimbursement form
for this project.

355
00:20:12,820 --> 00:20:14,050
The Finance Department was rushing me.

356
00:20:14,050 --> 00:20:15,150
I can't push you to get this done.

357
00:20:15,360 --> 00:20:16,760
Fill out and submit them yourself.

358
00:20:51,280 --> 00:20:53,010
Pang Jing, what's wrong with you?

359
00:20:53,730 --> 00:20:55,080
What's wrong with this receipt?

360
00:20:55,080 --> 00:20:56,830
The amount and time do not match.

361
00:20:56,840 --> 00:20:58,760
This is irrelevant to our project.

362
00:20:59,840 --> 00:21:02,010
I made a mistake.

363
00:21:02,010 --> 00:21:03,420
You're such a meticulous person.

364
00:21:03,420 --> 00:21:04,460
How can you make a mistake?

365
00:21:04,560 --> 00:21:06,520
I'm afraid
you want to take advantage of the FD

366
00:21:06,520 --> 00:21:08,450
and try to get more reimbursement.

367
00:21:09,800 --> 00:21:11,160
I made a mistake

368
00:21:11,160 --> 00:21:13,010
because you were bragging in the office.

369
00:21:13,010 --> 00:21:14,650
How's that my fault?

370
00:21:15,120 --> 00:21:16,010
Listen.

371
00:21:16,010 --> 00:21:18,010
Luckily, I reviewed this receipt today.

372
00:21:18,160 --> 00:21:19,560
Otherwise,
no one would find out about it.

373
00:21:20,250 --> 00:21:22,080
Even when we only had
a small budget for this project,

374
00:21:22,080 --> 00:21:22,990
you tried to reimburse more.

375
00:21:23,020 --> 00:21:24,180
What about the other projects?

376
00:21:24,180 --> 00:21:25,890
God knows how much more
you've reimbursed.

377
00:21:26,280 --> 00:21:28,830
I didn't. Stop your slander!

378
00:21:28,840 --> 00:21:31,600
You should do your work
sincerely and honestly.

379
00:21:31,850 --> 00:21:33,280
In our office,

380
00:21:33,490 --> 00:21:34,720
your colleagues and leaders

381
00:21:34,730 --> 00:21:37,120
will keep their eyes on you.

382
00:21:37,280 --> 00:21:38,560
Now I'm the team leader.

383
00:21:38,790 --> 00:21:40,890
I'll closely monitor such behavior.

384
00:21:40,890 --> 00:21:42,560
I won't allow this to happen again.

385
00:21:42,980 --> 00:21:45,080
How much damage will it do
to the company?

386
00:21:45,360 --> 00:21:46,840
You need
to take care of your work attitude.

387
00:21:47,160 --> 00:21:48,360
(After three days of insomnia,)

388
00:21:48,360 --> 00:21:49,840
(the constant release of adrenaline)

389
00:21:50,280 --> 00:21:52,210
(has caused Xiuya's blood pressure
to rise.)

390
00:21:52,460 --> 00:21:55,000
(She experiences arrhythmia
and loses control over her emotions.)

391
00:21:55,320 --> 00:21:56,490
(She did something)

392
00:21:56,490 --> 00:21:58,080
(even she couldn't have imagined.)

393
00:21:59,760 --> 00:22:02,000
Ma Chao, you're the one
who has a wrongful work attitude.

394
00:22:10,260 --> 00:22:11,770
Wu Xiuya, did you take the wrong pills?

395
00:22:12,360 --> 00:22:14,010
She indeed had too much coffee.

396
00:22:14,800 --> 00:22:17,450
Answer me. Have you made even
one chart in the bidding proposal?

397
00:22:17,460 --> 00:22:19,730
Do you know anything about
consumer habits and preferences

398
00:22:19,730 --> 00:22:20,620
in the beverage market?

399
00:22:20,740 --> 00:22:22,250
When Pang Jing and I were working late,

400
00:22:22,250 --> 00:22:24,280
have you ever asked
if we needed any help?

401
00:22:24,560 --> 00:22:26,560
You hid behind our backs when working.

402
00:22:26,560 --> 00:22:27,440
Good for you.

403
00:22:27,450 --> 00:22:29,400
When claiming the credit,
you rush to the front.

404
00:22:29,420 --> 00:22:31,280
That's your work attitude?

405
00:22:31,930 --> 00:22:32,970
Xiuya, calm down.

406
00:22:32,970 --> 00:22:35,010
- No need arguing with him.
- Right.

407
00:22:35,280 --> 00:22:37,560
The proposal was indeed
recognized by the leaders.

408
00:22:37,660 --> 00:22:38,920
You should take credit for that.

409
00:22:38,920 --> 00:22:40,560
Indeed, as for this,

410
00:22:40,560 --> 00:22:42,490
I emphasized it to the Chairman.

411
00:22:42,490 --> 00:22:43,560
If it weren't for me,

412
00:22:43,560 --> 00:22:45,110
everyone would think that you're here

413
00:22:45,120 --> 00:22:46,970
because of your boyfriend's connections.

414
00:22:46,970 --> 00:22:47,810
Ma Chao.

415
00:22:48,280 --> 00:22:50,760
I used to think you're just lazy.

416
00:22:51,130 --> 00:22:52,860
I didn't expect you to be so petty.

417
00:22:52,860 --> 00:22:54,190
- Watch your mouth.
- Others don't know,

418
00:22:54,190 --> 00:22:55,680
but colleagues from our department
know well.

419
00:22:55,680 --> 00:22:57,010
You become the team leader

420
00:22:57,010 --> 00:22:59,010
because of this proposal.

421
00:22:59,250 --> 00:23:01,800
Answer me. How did you contribute to it?

422
00:23:01,800 --> 00:23:03,160
By playing games?

423
00:23:03,160 --> 00:23:04,320
Or by taking advantage of us?

424
00:23:04,490 --> 00:23:06,120
I can't tolerate this.

425
00:23:06,120 --> 00:23:07,520
How did I become the team leader?

426
00:23:07,520 --> 00:23:08,560
I don't even know myself.

427
00:23:08,580 --> 00:23:10,240
Besides, you said it was
because of the proposal.

428
00:23:10,240 --> 00:23:11,560
That is just your guess, isn't it?

429
00:23:11,560 --> 00:23:13,520
Of course it's because of the proposal.

430
00:23:13,520 --> 00:23:15,360
You've been a specialist for five years.

431
00:23:15,360 --> 00:23:17,030
How come you suddenly became
a team leader

432
00:23:17,030 --> 00:23:18,070
after you met the Chairman?

433
00:23:18,070 --> 00:23:20,250
I'd like to ask myself.

434
00:23:20,250 --> 00:23:22,280
What does it take
to get promoted to team leader?

435
00:23:22,440 --> 00:23:24,560
Let's go ask Mr. Gao.

436
00:23:24,970 --> 00:23:25,840
Let's go.

437
00:23:37,560 --> 00:23:38,460
As I promised.

438
00:23:38,460 --> 00:23:39,430
Let's get straight to it.

439
00:23:39,430 --> 00:23:40,560
Thank you for your hard work.

440
00:23:40,560 --> 00:23:41,520
One for each of you.

441
00:23:45,400 --> 00:23:46,280
Thank you, Hao.

442
00:23:46,360 --> 00:23:47,670
Thank you, Hao.

443
00:23:47,680 --> 00:23:48,840
Hao bought these

444
00:23:48,850 --> 00:23:50,010
with his own commission.

445
00:23:51,600 --> 00:23:52,450
Keep a low profile.

446
00:23:52,450 --> 00:23:54,250
Don't let other departments find out.

447
00:23:55,010 --> 00:23:56,120
Why are you holding this?

448
00:23:56,410 --> 00:23:57,280
I want to keep one.

449
00:23:57,280 --> 00:23:58,560
This is for my Xiuya.

450
00:23:58,560 --> 00:24:00,010
You've got yours already.

451
00:24:00,360 --> 00:24:01,650
Hao is the model boyfriend.

452
00:24:01,650 --> 00:24:03,120
When will you marry our sister-in-law?

453
00:24:05,560 --> 00:24:06,650
Don't rush.

454
00:24:06,940 --> 00:24:07,840
Soon.

455
00:24:08,450 --> 00:24:10,080
Zhang Yan moved faster.

456
00:24:10,360 --> 00:24:11,970
You should all come to my wedding

457
00:24:12,160 --> 00:24:13,590
- and give me wedding gifts.
- Sure.

458
00:24:14,800 --> 00:24:15,640
Hello.

459
00:24:16,450 --> 00:24:17,290
Ms. Hu.

460
00:24:44,080 --> 00:24:45,320
(This argument)

461
00:24:45,760 --> 00:24:47,280
(has drained the last drop of energy)

462
00:24:47,280 --> 00:24:49,250
(from Wu Xiuya.)

463
00:24:53,250 --> 00:24:55,520
(She's now like a flattened balloon.)

464
00:24:56,010 --> 00:24:58,010
(She's even too tired to talk.)

465
00:25:09,140 --> 00:25:10,760
(Zheng Hao)

466
00:25:10,760 --> 00:25:12,380
Let's eat at this place
together tonight.

467
00:25:12,380 --> 00:25:13,310
I've made a reservation.

468
00:25:13,310 --> 00:25:15,120
You go first.
I'll go straight from the client's place.

469
00:25:52,010 --> 00:25:53,560
I've always wanted to bring you here.

470
00:25:53,840 --> 00:25:55,280
But I'm either on a business trip

471
00:25:55,280 --> 00:25:56,490
or I can't make a reservation.

472
00:25:56,490 --> 00:25:57,450
Finally, we're here.

473
00:25:57,560 --> 00:25:58,520
Have a try. Is it good?

474
00:26:02,010 --> 00:26:02,850
It's good.

475
00:26:03,280 --> 00:26:04,230
Have more if it's good.

476
00:26:04,230 --> 00:26:05,780
Filling your stomach improves your mood.

477
00:26:06,840 --> 00:26:08,250
I haven't seen you for two days.

478
00:26:08,360 --> 00:26:09,250
What happened to you?

479
00:26:09,490 --> 00:26:10,800
Why do you look so tired?

480
00:26:11,480 --> 00:26:12,320
I didn't sleep well.

481
00:26:12,990 --> 00:26:14,210
You should get some rest.

482
00:26:17,490 --> 00:26:18,600
Ms. Hu just called me.

483
00:26:18,760 --> 00:26:20,260
She told me what happened

484
00:26:20,260 --> 00:26:21,420
in your office this afternoon.

485
00:26:21,650 --> 00:26:22,970
I didn't believe her at first.

486
00:26:23,840 --> 00:26:24,820
I said,

487
00:26:24,820 --> 00:26:26,440
"how can my Xiuya do something like this?"

488
00:26:28,120 --> 00:26:29,360
I indeed did it.

489
00:26:29,870 --> 00:26:31,250
How do you plan to take care of it?

490
00:26:37,560 --> 00:26:38,800
The HRBP said

491
00:26:38,800 --> 00:26:40,210
they would investigate this.

492
00:26:40,370 --> 00:26:41,760
Manager Hu saw the whole thing.

493
00:26:42,560 --> 00:26:43,800
Since she called you,

494
00:26:43,800 --> 00:26:46,280
you should be the one telling me
how to handle this.

495
00:26:46,430 --> 00:26:47,700
Now you ask me.

496
00:26:48,460 --> 00:26:49,890
Did Manager Hu request you to ask me?

497
00:26:50,970 --> 00:26:53,210
I think you already know
what you should do.

498
00:26:53,450 --> 00:26:54,290
What should I do?

499
00:26:54,730 --> 00:26:55,890
You don't need me to tell you.

500
00:26:56,840 --> 00:26:58,010
You'd better tell me

501
00:26:58,250 --> 00:26:59,600
in case we think differently.

502
00:27:01,280 --> 00:27:02,120
Fine.

503
00:27:02,680 --> 00:27:04,800
I'll analyze this incident for you
from the beginning.

504
00:27:05,210 --> 00:27:07,010
According to what you
and Manager Hu told me,

505
00:27:07,010 --> 00:27:09,210
Ma Chao is bad and stupid.

506
00:27:09,280 --> 00:27:10,160
He's not well-liked.

507
00:27:10,160 --> 00:27:11,320
And he's not good at his work.

508
00:27:11,400 --> 00:27:12,280
That's why

509
00:27:12,280 --> 00:27:13,730
he hasn't been promoted for years.

510
00:27:14,070 --> 00:27:15,970
But that's how you underestimated him.

511
00:27:15,970 --> 00:27:17,120
He's got one thing

512
00:27:17,120 --> 00:27:18,840
that none of you have.

513
00:27:19,040 --> 00:27:19,880
He's shameless.

514
00:27:20,490 --> 00:27:22,080
If a person has no principles,

515
00:27:22,080 --> 00:27:23,560
it's hard for others to beat him.

516
00:27:25,360 --> 00:27:26,630
He probably could only play smart

517
00:27:27,010 --> 00:27:28,360
for a brief moment.

518
00:27:28,360 --> 00:27:29,560
But he found the right moment.

519
00:27:33,060 --> 00:27:33,990
Change your perspective.

520
00:27:33,990 --> 00:27:35,490
If you were your department manager,

521
00:27:35,510 --> 00:27:36,820
what would you say to the Chairman

522
00:27:36,820 --> 00:27:37,840
under that circumstance?

523
00:27:37,980 --> 00:27:39,260
Yes, Ma Chao was wrong.

524
00:27:39,260 --> 00:27:41,060
This is done by another employee
from our department.

525
00:27:41,160 --> 00:27:43,160
How the Chairman
and other department heads

526
00:27:43,160 --> 00:27:44,480
would think about your department?

527
00:27:44,480 --> 00:27:46,720
There is a conflict of interest
inside your department.

528
00:27:46,730 --> 00:27:48,480
And you had a confrontation
in front of the Chairman.

529
00:27:48,730 --> 00:27:51,010
Then you won't get any credit
for the proposal.

530
00:27:51,010 --> 00:27:53,210
Ms. Hu would get scolded as well.

531
00:27:53,360 --> 00:27:55,600
I understand that Manager Hu was
in a difficult position.

532
00:27:55,600 --> 00:27:56,960
So I didn't say anything that day.

533
00:27:56,960 --> 00:27:58,700
But when the HRBP came
to talk to Manager Hu

534
00:27:58,700 --> 00:28:00,840
about Ma Chao's promotion today,

535
00:28:00,840 --> 00:28:02,890
Manager Hu still won't tell the truth.

536
00:28:02,890 --> 00:28:03,800
That's not fair.

537
00:28:04,280 --> 00:28:05,450
Mr. Gao was there

538
00:28:05,450 --> 00:28:07,450
at the command of the HR Director.

539
00:28:07,450 --> 00:28:09,890
After all, he was just carrying out
the Chairman's orders.

540
00:28:10,160 --> 00:28:11,900
If you tell him
these misunderstandings now,

541
00:28:11,900 --> 00:28:13,480
Mr. Gao will be
in a difficult position.

542
00:28:13,490 --> 00:28:15,010
Think about it. When Mr. Gao knows,

543
00:28:15,010 --> 00:28:16,600
he has to report to his leader.

544
00:28:16,600 --> 00:28:17,520
If he does,

545
00:28:17,520 --> 00:28:19,210
that's insulting to the HR Director.

546
00:28:19,210 --> 00:28:20,640
Vice versa, the HR Director

547
00:28:20,640 --> 00:28:21,760
can't report to the Chairman.

548
00:28:21,760 --> 00:28:23,760
Because if he does,

549
00:28:23,760 --> 00:28:25,320
