819
00:40:14,200 --> 00:40:15,720
Because it was Ma Chao's fault.

820
00:40:16,370 --> 00:40:18,240
If this mistake is not corrected,

821
00:40:19,010 --> 00:40:22,080
how are we supposed to devote ourselves

822
00:40:22,450 --> 00:40:25,370
wholeheartedly to our work
in the future?

823
00:40:27,160 --> 00:40:28,720
That's all I have to say.

824
00:40:41,930 --> 00:40:43,120
This is the end of the matter.

825
00:40:45,200 --> 00:40:46,120
I have a few words.

826
00:40:46,890 --> 00:40:47,820
I'm certainly willing to

827
00:40:47,920 --> 00:40:50,200
let you express your true feelings here,

828
00:40:50,560 --> 00:40:52,030
as long as it doesn't affect our work.

829
00:40:52,850 --> 00:40:55,490
But what's most important at work is,

830
00:40:55,730 --> 00:40:58,240
despite the discrepancies,

831
00:40:58,740 --> 00:41:01,520
we must learn to agree to disagree.

832
00:41:04,160 --> 00:41:05,000
Dismissed.

833
00:41:28,970 --> 00:41:29,960
(Insomnia has become)

834
00:41:29,960 --> 00:41:32,080
(one of the most serious health problems
of our time.)

835
00:41:32,330 --> 00:41:33,370
(In every five people,)

836
00:41:33,720 --> 00:41:35,720
(one would suffer from insomnia.)

837
00:41:36,120 --> 00:41:38,050
(Some people believe
that urban life has changed)

838
00:41:38,050 --> 00:41:40,060
(how people work and rest
over the past centuries.)

839
00:41:40,450 --> 00:41:41,390
(Others believe that)

840
00:41:41,390 --> 00:41:44,090
(soaring stress causes a sharp increase
in the number of insomniacs.)

841
00:41:44,560 --> 00:41:46,490
(There's no scientific basis for this.)

842
00:41:46,640 --> 00:41:48,930
(But after speaking from her heart
in public,)

843
00:41:49,490 --> 00:41:51,490
(Wu Xiuya got rid
of her mental pressure.)

844
00:41:51,770 --> 00:41:53,560
(Now she reclaimed her sleep.)

845
00:42:17,601 --> 00:42:22,051
♪Close the comic books,
store apples in the fridge♪

846
00:42:22,051 --> 00:42:25,911
♪Nerves are numb and itchy♪

847
00:42:26,201 --> 00:42:30,701
♪Stop messing around
and put away the smile♪

848
00:42:30,701 --> 00:42:34,601
♪Even mad but don't be forced to smile♪

849
00:42:35,051 --> 00:42:39,411
♪People's characters change♪

850
00:42:39,411 --> 00:42:43,211
♪As time passes and tastes change♪

851
00:42:43,621 --> 00:42:48,081
♪Just laugh without caring for elegance♪

852
00:42:48,081 --> 00:42:52,071
♪Be unique, don't be ordinary♪

853
00:42:52,071 --> 00:42:56,101
♪Let go of lasting memories,
be grateful♪

854
00:42:56,371 --> 00:43:00,701
♪Let go of all struggles
and stubbornness♪

855
00:43:00,701 --> 00:43:04,981
♪Fill the house with freedom. Be free♪

856
00:43:04,981 --> 00:43:08,291
♪Let go of childhood dreams♪

857
00:43:08,291 --> 00:43:11,371
♪And hesitations♪

858
00:43:27,081 --> 00:43:31,471
♪Don't need a broad shoulder
to cry over♪

859
00:43:31,471 --> 00:43:35,201
♪Tears sink into the soil♪

860
00:43:35,571 --> 00:43:40,041
♪Grow into a tree where birds nest♪

861
00:43:40,041 --> 00:43:43,811
♪Passersby, put aside your worries♪

862
00:43:44,071 --> 00:43:48,131
♪Let stars and moon shine
in tomorrow's night sky♪

863
00:43:48,351 --> 00:43:52,401
♪Let sorrows float into the creek♪

864
00:43:52,691 --> 00:43:56,741
♪Let fearless courage flow into the air♪

865
00:43:56,971 --> 00:44:01,471
♪Let the lovely gaze
linger on your face♪

866
